acknowledgment_letter.body:
Dear {requester_name},

This letter acknowledges receipt of your request under the Municipal Freedom of Information and Protection of Privacy Act (MFIPPA) received on {received_date}.

Your request has been assigned the following reference number: {tracking_number}

Please use this reference number in all future correspondence regarding this request.

Your request is for: {request_description}

Under MFIPPA, we have 30 days to respond to your request. We will make every effort to provide you with the requested information within this timeframe.

If you have any questions, please contact us at {contact_email}.

Sincerely,
{org_name}
Freedom of Information Coordinator

fee_estimate.body:
Dear {requester_name},

Re: Freedom of Information Request {tracking_number}

We have completed our review of your request and determined that fees will apply.

Estimated fees:
- Search time: {search_hours} hours @ $7.50/hour = ${search_cost}
- Preparation time: {prep_hours} hours @ $7.50/hour = ${prep_cost}
- Photocopying: {page_count} pages @ $0.20/page = ${copy_cost}

Total estimated fee: ${total_fee}

The first $5.00 is waived. Amount owing: ${amount_owing}

Please note:
- A 50% deposit of ${deposit_amount} is required before we proceed
- Final fees may vary from this estimate
- You have 30 days to respond to this fee estimate

To proceed with your request, please send payment to:
{org_name}
{payment_address}

If you have questions about these fees, please contact us at {contact_email}.

Sincerely,
{org_name}
Freedom of Information Coordinator

redaction_analysis.user_prompt_template:
Analyze this document for MFIPPA exemptions. Identify information that should be severed under sections 6-14.

Document text:
{document_text}

For each exemption, provide:
1. The exact text to sever
2. The MFIPPA section (s6-s14)
3. Brief reason
4. Confidence level (high/medium/low)

Return as JSON:
{
  "suggestions": [
    {
      "text": "exact text",
      "category": "s14",
      "reason": "Personal information - name and address",
      "confidence": "high"
    }
  ],
  "summary": "Overall analysis"
}
